room_title: Escape room "The Lost Antidote" by The Escape Omaha in Omaha
review: My friends and I did the Antidote escape room and finished with 10+ minutes to spare. All the puzzles were fairly straightforward, but there was some diversity in them as well. I’d definitely recommend this place if you’re looking for a group activity.

room_title: Escape room "The Lost Antidote" by The Escape Omaha in Omaha
review: We filled the Lost Antidote room with a group ranging in age from 8-38. This room was perfect for us as everyone could be involved and we made it out successfully. The staff was kind and easy to work with! And reset the room quickly for us to be able to enter.

room_title: Escape room "The Lost Antidote" by The Escape Omaha in Omaha
review: The Lost Antidote is my fourth room I've done with The Escape...always a great time but this room was amazing. Kudos to the team!

room_title: Escape room "The Lost Antidote" by The Escape Omaha in Omaha
review: Went there with my family to celebrate the wife's birthday. We did "The Lost Antidote" and had a blast! (And we successfully solved it too) The staff was great to work with! We already have plans to come back and do another one.
